@loyalty
title: Increase militia cooperation with the Soviet.
on-arrival: workers_militia_m_loyalty += 5 if player_party = "m"; workers_militia_sr_loyalty += 5 if player_party = "sr"; workers_militia_b_loyalty += 5 if player_party = "b"

We have increased the direction of the Soviet parties over the workers' militias.

