We have increased recruitment into the workers' militias.

@arming
title: Increase armaments for the militias.
subtitle: -1 resource
choose-if: workers_militia_militancy < 0.7 and ((player_party = "m" and m_resources >= 1) or (player_party = "sr" and sr_resources >= 1) or (player_party = "b" and b_resources >= 1))
unavailable-subtitle: [? if ((player_party = "m" and m_resources < 1) or (player_party = "sr" and sr_resources < 1) or (player_party = "b" and b_resources < 1)): We do not have enough resources. ?]
on-arrival: workers_militia_militancy += 0.05; sr_resources -= 1 if player_party = "sr"; b_resources -= 1 if player_party = "b"; m_resources -= 1 if player_party = "m";

We have spent resources on purchasing more armaments for the workers' militias.

@mrc
title: Form a Military-Revolutionary Committee!
subtitle: We will organize the workers' militias for the defense of the revolution against all enemies. -2 resources
unavailable-subtitle: -2 resources 
view-if: player_party = "b"
choose-if: b_resources >= 2
on-arrival: soldiers_b += 15; workers_militia_b_loyalty += 25; mrc = 1;
max-visits: 1

The Petrograd Soviet has formed the Military-Revolutionary Committee, a committee to organize the workers' militias and garrison troops for the defense of the revolution.

